item.title: Spawning help~
item.dc:creator: @pleya2 pleya2
item.description:
@pleya2 wrote:

[quote=“IcyPimp, post:3, topic:17705”][quote author=pleya2 link=topic=26573.msg302444#msg302444 date=1160453475]
To sawn on a server you must either be admin or Owner

if you have a server just type either ::item 4151 4151= whip what item does is spawn it on the floor
or ::pickup 4151 1 this means the item will spawn in your inventory 1 is the amount to have just see if the item is notable which in this case a noted whip is 4152 so if you wanted 20 whips noted you would type ::pickup 4152 20
[/quote]

Nope…if the owner deleted the && playerrights thing in client.java, anyone can use it, which is what he is talking about.[/quote]

then he/she can use the other info i gave on how to spawn…
